==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: bennie
<hw>ben"nie</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a slang name for Benzedrine, a
trademark for one brand of amphetamine; -- also used generically for any
brand of amphetamine.</def> <mark>[slang]</mark> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>benny</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Benzedrine.</syn>⟦br⟧
